data.description: Entertainers Dream! Move-In Ready Single Story Home Features 3 Bedrooms & 2 Bathrooms & Sits on 1/4 Acre Lot, Built in 2008. Property is Zoned to Add an Additional Unit with an Alley Access or can be used for RV Parking in the Rear of the Property. Newer Vinyl Fencing in the Backyard. Open Flor Plan! Spacious Kitchen Featuring Granite Counter Tops & Newer Black Appliances.  Updated Light Fixtures & Ceiling Fans in all the Bedrooms. Double Sided Fireplace Faces the Entry Way & Family Room. Spacious Master Bedroom with a Large Walk-In Closet. The Bathroom Features Granite Counter Tops, Dual Sinks, & a Separate Shower & Bathtub. Indoor Laundry Room & an Attached 2 Car Garage. Come See Why It's Not Just a House It's Your Home!
